{"id":173855,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":1,"day":3}],"page":"5","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"302","ytitle":"","mtitle":"界限与判决","ftitle":"","authors":["谢泗春"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢泗春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝还是山姆叔的气焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主恶霸还是虎狼般的嘴脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刮民匪帮还在伪装和平，图延残喘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广大人民在反动淫威下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢怒而不敢言!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民主、和平、欢乐、幸福的新册，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经开卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广大人民已从泥潭中把身翻转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建立起自己的国家自己的政权!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸿沟虽宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些家伙们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的已尸横道边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的已涕泣涟涟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的已打青脸面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狼奔豕突，窜出中国美丽的花园!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专划、混乱、悲惨、恐怖的旧戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在续演，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"止于分清楚汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那及今年今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晰划出新旧中国的明暗面；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌江之刎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"止于标明项灭刘兴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那及今年今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远宣判着新旧中国一切的毁灭与萌生!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我没有见过这么明确广阔的界限，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我没有见过这么伟大庄严的判决!"}]}